2 An act relating to expanding employee access to unpaid leave
3 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
4 Sec. 1. INTENT
5 It is the intent of the General Assembly to align Vermont’s family leave
6 policies with inclusive and equitable standards, ensuring that LGBTQ+
7 families, workers with low income, and individuals in nontraditional family
8 structures have equal access to caregiving leave without undue burden.
